<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als wir nehst <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        erber <expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> zu <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> gesandt <expan>hette<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        von der <expan>anlangu<ex>n</ex>g</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> der stewre, die
                            <expan>etlich<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> und der <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>lewt<ex>en</ex></expan> und <expan>gut<ex>en</ex></expan> von
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>amptlewt<ex>en</ex></expan> beschehen und ewr gnade
                                <expan>ders<ex>elben</ex></expan> sache
                            <expan>ein<ex>en</ex></expan> aufslag gab uncz auf den <app>
<note><q type="date">sunntag
                                        <expan>remi<ex>ni</ex>sce<ex>re</ex></expan>
                                schierist</q>08.03.1422</note>
</app>, also <expan>wolte<ex>n</ex></expan> wir seid
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> zu <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürstenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> geschikt <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>, so hat
                        uns merklich sache gesawmt. So <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir auch nu
                                <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz ewr
                                <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> auf den
                                <expan>nehst<ex>en</ex></expan> sunntag zu
                            <expan>eine<ex>m</ex></expan> tag gen Kiczing
                            <expan>geford<ex>er</ex>t</expan> sey und <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>w<ex>er</ex>de</expan>, also daz wir besorgt
                            <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> ewr gnade yecz mit muss niht
                                <expan>finde<ex>n</ex></expan> möcht. <expan>Daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> wir ewr <expan>fürstenl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
                        gnade mit fleisz, ir wellet <expan>dies<ex>elb</ex></expan> sache umb
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> willen
                            <expan>aufslahe<ex>n</ex></expan> und mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>amptlewt<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>bestelle<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz der <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                        lewt und <expan>güt<ex>er</ex></expan> mit rwen
                            <expan>beleibe<ex>n</ex></expan>. Wenn sich denn ewr
                                <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> hernach zu den
                                <expan>sache<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>müssige<ex>n</ex></expan> meynt, so <expan>welle<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        wir <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> erber <expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> zu
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden <expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        und <expan>getrawe<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> wol, ir <expan>v<ex>er</ex>czeiht</expan> uns
                        der bett niht. Denn wo wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> dienst und wolgefallen etc. Und
                                <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> ewr gnedig
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> antwurt, ob uns ewr gnade möcht
                                <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan>, wenn wir ewr gnade mit muss
                                <expan>finde<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>möchte<ex>n</ex></expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut
                                <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
